| **新增** `src/__tests__/workspace/workspace-inspector.test.ts` | 覆盖：git repo / non-git / dirty tree / baseline / untracked 文件 / stash create 失败 | all |
| **改** `src/__tests__/session/context-manager.test.ts` | 增加：diff 注入 / 自定义模板无 `{{codeDiff}}` 自动追加 / 分段预算截断 | #3, #4 |
| **改** `src/__tests__/session/session-resume.test.ts` | 增加：恢复时 diff 可用 / 恢复时 diff 不可用降级 | #2 |

### 数据流总览

```
Session Start
  └→ captureBaseline() → sessionBaseline (git rev-parse HEAD or null)

Each Round:
  CODING → coder LLM executes
  ↓
  ROUTING_POST_CODE → route decision (同步，不改)
  ↓
  CAPTURING_DIFF → WorkspaceInspector.captureDiff(projectDir, roundBaseline)
  │                 ├─ git repo:  tracked diff + untracked file preview
  │                 └─ non-git:   { available: false, strategy: 'non-git' }
  │
  │  persist codeDiff to HistoryEntry (role=coder)
  │  send DIFF_CAPTURED / DIFF_SKIPPED
  ↓
  REVIEWING → buildReviewerPrompt(task, rounds, coderOutput, { codeDiff })
  │            ├─ 默认模板: {{codeDiff}} 替换
  │            ├─ 自定义模板有 {{codeDiff}}: 替换
  │            └─ 自定义模板无 {{codeDiff}}: 自动追加 ## Actual Code Changes
  │            → enforceTokenBudget (分段预算，保护审查规则)
  ↓
  EVALUATING → roundsRef.push({ ..., codeDiff, diffSummary })

Resume:
  history.jsonl → HistoryEntry.codeDiff → buildRounds → RoundRecord.codeDiff
  → buildRestoredSessionRuntime → workflowInput.lastCodeDiff
  → RESTORED_TO_REVIEWING → reviewer prompt 使用恢复的 diff
```

### 一句话总结

把 Duo 从"基于 LLM 文本叙述的对话转发器"升级为"基于真实工作区变更的代码审查平台"——通过中间状态 `CAPTURING_DIFF` 消除竞态、完整 diff 持久化支持 resume、分段预算保护审查规则不被截断、自定义模板自动追加兼容、untracked 新文件纳入变更面、非 git 环境 graceful fallback。

