### 数据流总览（v4 最终版）

```
Session Start
  └→ App.tsx 初始化 lastDiffRef = null

Each Round:
  CODING → coder LLM 执行
  │  成功: addHistoryEntry(coder, content) ← 不动，即时持久化
  │  send(CODE_COMPLETE)
  ↓
  ROUTING_POST_CODE → decidePostCodeRoute() → send(ROUTE_TO_CAPTURE_DIFF)
  ↓
  CAPTURING_DIFF → WorkspaceInspector.captureDiff(projectDir)
  │  ├─ git: tracked diff + untracked preview
  │  └─ non-git: { available: false }
  │
  │  saveDiffArtifact(sessionId, round, result)  ← 独立文件
  │  addHistoryEntry 补 diffSummary 到 coder entry ← 可选，轻量
  │  lastDiffRef.current = result
  │  send(DIFF_CAPTURED / DIFF_SKIPPED)
  ↓
  REVIEWING → buildReviewerPrompt(task, rounds, coderOutput, { codeDiff })
  │  ├─ 默认模板: {{codeDiff}} 替换
  │  ├─ 自定义模板有 {{codeDiff}}: 替换
  │  └─ 自定义模板无 {{codeDiff}}: 自动追加 ## Actual Code Changes
  │  → enforceTokenBudget (分段预算: 保护 Review Criteria / Verdict)
  ↓
  EVALUATING → roundsRef.push({ ..., diffSummary })

Resume:
  snapshot.status = 'capturing_diff' → mapRestoreEvent → RESTORED_TO_REVIEWING
  App.tsx 恢复路径: loadDiffArtifact(sessionId, lastRound) → lastDiffRef
  → REVIEWING effect 使用恢复的 diff（文件存在）或 null（文件丢失 = graceful degradation）
```

